OL,3,CMystery of how giant galaxies formed
OL,4,Ccould be close to being solved
OL,6,FGalaxies crashing together 12 billion
OL,7,Fyears ago could have caused the
OL,8,Funiverse's biggest galaxies to form,
OL,9,Faccording to new research.
OL,11,FA study by astronomers at the
OL,12,FUniversity of Southampton is hoping to
OL,13,Fsolve what they are calling an
OL,14,F"intergalactic mystery" of how
OL,15,Felliptical galaxies were created up to
OL,16,F12 billion years ago.
