OL,3,CMystery of how giant galaxies formed
OL,4,Ccould be close to being solved
OL,6,FHow these galaxies, which look similar
OL,7,Fto bulging footballs compared with the
OL,8,Fflat disc of the Milky Way, emerged,
OL,9,Fhas been at the centre of research for
OL,10,Fdecades.
OL,12,FBut Dr Annagrazia Puglisi has said in
OL,13,Fa paper published in the journal
OL,14,FNature that the team are now close to
OL,15,Fcoming to an answer.
OL,17,FShe said: "Two disc galaxies smashing
OL,18,Ftogether caused gas, the fuel from
OL,19,Fwhich stars are formed, to sink
OL,20,Ftowards their centre, generating
OL,21,Ftrillions of new stars.
