OL,3,CMystery of how giant galaxies formed
OL,4,Ccould be close to being solved
OL,6,F"These cosmic collisions happened some
OL,7,Feight to 12 billion years ago, when
OL,8,Fthe universe was in a much more active
OL,9,Fphase of its evolution.
OL,11,F"Our findings take us closer to
OL,12,Fsolving a long-standing mystery in
OL,13,Fastronomy that will redefine our
OL,14,Funderstanding of how galaxies were
OL,15,Fcreated in the early universe."
