OL,3,CMystery of how giant galaxies formed
OL,4,Ccould be close to being solved
OL,6,FShe said: "This is the first real
OL,7,Fevidence that spheroids form directly
OL,8,Fthrough intense episodes of star
OL,9,Fformation located in the cores of
OL,10,Fdistant galaxies.
OL,12,F"Astrophysicists have sought to
OL,13,Funderstand this process for decades.
OL,15,F"These galaxies form quickly ` gas is
OL,16,Fsucked inwards to feed black holes and
OL,17,Ftriggers bursts of stars, which are
OL,18,Fcreated at rates 10 to 100 times
OL,19,Ffaster than our Milky Way."
