OL,3,CMystery of how giant galaxies formed
OL,4,Ccould be close to being solved
OL,6,FThe scientists will now combine their
OL,7,Ffindings with data taken from
OL,8,Ftelescopes aboard the James Webb and
OL,9,FEuclid satellites, and the Chinese
OL,10,FSpace Station, to map the stellar
OL,11,Fcomponents of galaxies.
OL,13,FDr Puglisi said: "This will give us a
OL,14,Fmore complete picture of early galaxy
OL,15,Fformation and deepen our understanding
OL,16,Fof how the universe has evolved since
OL,17,Fthe beginning of time."
